# Between technical test

## How to start the project and test it
### 1-Clone de project
### 2-Install all dependencies:
In the root
<pre>
npm i
</pre>
 ### 3-Run the project
In the root
<pre>
npm start
</pre>
### 4- For run the test
In the root
<pre>
npm run test
</pre>
